==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Nyentek
<hw>Ny*en"tek</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos> <fld>(Zool.)</fld>
<def>A carnivorous mammal (<spn>Helictis moscatus</spn>, or
<spn>Helictis orientalis</spn>), native of Eastern Asia and the Indies.
It has a dorsal white stripe, and another one across the shoulders. It
has a strong musky odor.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>nylghai</ent>⟦br⟧
